## Diagnostic Commands

### Docker Compose

```bash
# Service status
docker compose ps

# Service logs (follow mode)
docker compose logs -f <service>

# All service logs
docker compose logs

# Restart a service
docker compose restart <service>

# Rebuild and restart
docker compose up -d --build <service>
```

### Firewall (nftables)

```bash
# List full ruleset
sudo nft list ruleset

# List specific table
sudo nft list table inet filter

# List blocked IP sets
sudo nft list set inet filter blocked_v4
sudo nft list set inet filter blocked_v6

# Count rules
sudo nft list chain inet filter input

# Flush and reload
sudo nft flush ruleset
sudo nft -f /etc/nftables.conf
```

### Systemd Timers

```bash
# List all timers
systemctl list-timers --all

# Check specific timer
systemctl status blocklist-updater.timer
systemctl status hostname-resolver.timer
systemctl status certbot-renew.timer

# View service logs
journalctl -u blocklist-updater.service
journalctl -u hostname-resolver.service
journalctl -u certbot-renew.service
```

### TLS / Connectivity

```bash
# Test TLS connection
curl -v https://{{ domain }}/

# Test TLS with specific version
openssl s_client -connect {{ domain }}:443 -servername {{ domain }} -tls1_3

# Test Reality SNI target
openssl s_client -connect {{ reality_sni }}:443 -tls1_3 < /dev/null

# Check certificate details
echo | openssl s_client -connect {{ domain }}:443 -servername {{ domain }} 2>/dev/null | openssl x509 -noout -text

# Test Nginx configuration
docker compose exec reverse_proxy nginx -t
```

